# === Experiment 9-3 Environment Variable Example: Copy to .env and fill in your Key ===

# This experiment uses OpenAI Whisper (whisper-1) for ASR and OpenAI TTS (tts-1) to synthesize test audio.
OPENAI_API_KEY=your_openai_api_key_here

# Note: The original experiment in the book used Qwen2-Audio, but it currently has no directly callable key/endpoint.
# This experiment only uses audio endpoints (ASR whisper-1 / TTS tts-1), which are only available via direct OpenAI connection—
# OpenRouter only handles chat completions and has no audio endpoints, so you cannot fall back to OPENROUTER_API_KEY; you must use
# a direct OpenAI key. If you only want to verify the chunking/timing logic, run python demo.py --offline, which requires no key.
